metadata.name: Sky Adventure
metadata.description:
Murakami Vibes

Sky High

Stay Fly

Don't Die

Upon A cloud I doth do dream

Heaven above me and the great supreme

Have I lost my mind it sure does seem

Clouds as fluffy as whipped cream

But alas, monsters lie amongst the muck

To make my dream a nightmare, to make it suck,

What shall be the resolution of this scene?

A dirty mess, or something more clean?

To wake up early or to sleep in

Visions of imagination come up from within
